# Repo policy: track the files needed for a one-click Streamlit
# Community Cloud deploy of the v11 dashboard via the root
# ``streamlit_app.py``. Everything else stays local.
#
# Deploy tree (must be present on GitHub):
#   streamlit_app.py            <- entry point (auto-detected by Cloud)
#   requirements.txt            <- runtime deps
#   .streamlit/config.toml      <- theme + headless server settings
#   footprint_model.py          <- simulation engine (imported by v4 core)
#   configs/                    <- state JSON + UI presets (state-aware
#                                  scenario explorer reads these)
#   scenarios/                  <- per-state scenario trees
#   v4_streamlit_app/           <- v4 core (v11/core.py loads it dynamically)
#   v11_streamlit_app/          <- the dashboard itself
#   src/clearats/               <- band plumbing for the Scenario Explorer
#   results/*_quantiles.csv     <- cached MC quantiles for offline fallback

# ---- Python ----
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.so

# ---- Environments ----
.venv/
venv/
env/

# ---- OS junk ----
.DS_Store
__MACOSX/
**/__MACOSX/

# ---- IDE / editor ----
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp

# ---- Claude Code local state ----
.claude/
memory/
CLAUDE.md

# ---- Caches ----
cache/
**/cache/
.pytest_cache/
.ipynb_checkpoints/
**/.ipynb_checkpoints/

# ---- Backups ----
*.bak
*.bak.*

# ---- Personal / private documents ----
Annual Review Form*.pdf
*Annual Review*.pdf

# ---- Large draft / manuscript PDFs + zips ----
Traffic_Autonomy_Expansion_Shifts_Marginal_Energy_Costs*.pdf
Traffic_Autonomy_Expansion_Shifts_Marginal_Energy_Costs*.zip
*.zip

